name: IU
description:
Please consider to support me by buying me some coffee so I can make a new LoRA faster. I do open commissions there too if you want to make your own custom LoRA: My BMAC page

-> IU V2, V4

Trigger word: leejieun

Use CLIP SKIP 2. You may need to use HIRES FIX with denoise strength between 0.5-0.7, Hires steps 20-30 is good but you can use whatever you want. Upscaler use 4x Foolhardy Remacri or SWINIR 4x.

Best checkpoints/models to use:

Realistic: VisionGen, ChillOutMix, ArtEros, Snapdd00, Henrealmix

Fanart/painting style: Dreamshaper, LucidMix, SunshineMix, Majicmix

Use it wisely. I don't responsible for anything you generated with this LoRa.

Join KPOP Diffusion Discord: https://discord.gg/NrBDMX79Da
